{% comment %}
  PLAYMATE LABS — PAGE SETUP TOOL
  ================================
  Access this page at: /pages/setup
  (Create a page in Shopify Admin with handle: setup, template: setup)
  
  This tool creates all required pages for the Playmate Labs theme.
  It uses Shopify's built-in Liquid + redirects to create pages individually.
{% endcomment %}

<style>
  body { background: #1A0A06; color: #F5EFE6; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .setup-wrapper { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem; }
  .setup-logo { font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #C9A96E; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .subtitle { color: #9B8E85; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .page-grid { display: grid; gap: 1rem; }
  .page-item {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .page-item.exists { border-color: rgba(100,200,100,0.3); background: rgba(100,200,100,0.05); }
  .page-info h3 { margin: 0 0 0.25rem; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .page-info .handle { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #C9A96E; font-family: monospace; }
  .page-info .template { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #9B8E85; }
  .btn-create {
    background: #C9A96E;
    color: #1A0A06;
    border: none;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-create:hover { background: #DFC08A; }
  .btn-exists { background: rgba(100,200,100,0.2); color: #6DC87A; border: 1px solid rgba(100,200,100,0.3); padding: 0.6rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.85rem; white-space: nowrap; }
  .section-header { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9B8E85; padding: 0.5rem 0; margin-top: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .instructions {
    background: rgba(201,169,110,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .instructions h2 { color: #C9A96E; font-size: 1rem; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; }
  .instructions ol { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 2; }
  .instructions li { color: #BEB5AD; }
  .instructions code { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 0.1em 0.4em; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.85em; color: #C9A96E; }
  .admin-link { color: #C9A96E; text-decoration: none; }
  .admin-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #9B8E85; margin-top: 0.5rem; font-style: italic; }
</style>

<div class="setup-wrapper">
  <div class="setup-logo">Playmate Labs</div>
  <h1>Page Setup Tool</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Create all required pages for the Playmate Labs theme. Click each link to open the Shopify admin page creator with the correct settings pre-filled.</p>

  <div class="instructions">
    <h2>📋 How to use this tool</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Click <strong>"Create in Admin"</strong> for each page below</li>
      <li>In the Shopify admin that opens, the page title will be pre-filled</li>
      <li>Set the <strong>Template</strong> dropdown to the value shown (e.g., <code>page.experience</code>)</li>
      <li>Click <strong>Save</strong></li>
      <li>The page will be live and linkable from your navigation!</li>
    </ol>
    <p class="note">💡 After creating pages, go to <a class="admin-link" href="/admin/menus" target="_blank">Online Store → Navigation</a> to add them to your menus.</p>
  </div>

